      },
      {
        "content": "Table 1 data for Group 2 shows that Charity successfully acquired the skill after 209 observations, with a total observation time of 69.38 hours and 23 solves. In contrast, other Group 2 members such as Carol (17 observations), Claire (0 observations), and Coco (3 observations) did not acquire the skill. The disparity between Charity’s success and the failure of others with lower observation counts reinforces the correlation between extensive social exposure and skill acquisition in this specific context.",
