      },
      {
        "content": "In Group 1, Rita is listed with 'NA' for observation metrics but recorded 1,970 solves, indicating she was likely the trained demonstrator or a pre-existing skilled individual whose observation data was not applicable in the same way as naive subjects. This outlier data point distinguishes her role from the naive learners and highlights the distinction between those transmitting the skill and those acquiring it.",
        "title": "Rita's status as a skilled individual in Group 1",
