      {
        "content": "The table provides a comprehensive list of Group 2 participants, revealing a wide disparity in observation times and rates. For instance, while some individuals like David had 0 hours of effective observation time, others like May had nearly 70 hours, reflecting the variable social dynamics and individual choices within the group during the experiment.",
