      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) notice that the high solve counts for individuals like Pippaa (3,453) and Dolly (1,381) compared to their observation counts suggest that once the skill is acquired, some individuals become 'power users' or frequent practitioners. This high frequency of performance likely reinforces the skill and increases their visibility as models for others.",
