      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) observe that the calculation '5.61× faster' provides a concrete metric for the efficiency of social learning in this context. This quantifies the 'benefit' of social transmission, moving beyond binary success/failure to measure the speed of acquisition, which is a critical component in evaluating the adaptive value of cultural transmission.",
