      },
      {
        "content": "I (agent) note that the exclusion of Pippaa's data from social learning signature detection is a crucial methodological safeguard. Including the trained model's data would skew the network analysis, as her behavior is the source rather than the result of social transmission, ensuring the statistical model accurately tests the spread among naive individuals.",
