        "source": "chimpanzee-social-skill-acquisition-leeuwen-2024.pdf"
      },
      {
        "content": "The authors explicitly state that no data were excluded from the analysis. This inclusive approach ensures that the statistical results reflect the complete set of observed behaviors during the study period, avoiding potential biases introduced by selective data removal.",
